data.title: Red Rock West Original 1993 British Quad Movie Poster
data.meta_description: Original 1993 British quad poster for the film Red Rock West directed by John Dahl with Nicolas Cage / Dennis Hopper / Lara Flynn Boyle / J.T. Walsh. Very Good-Fine condition, tri-fold. Many original posters were issued folded or were subsequently folded.
